to drive back to campus.

43
00:06:36,404 --> 00:06:38,531
That's all right.

44
00:06:44,278 --> 00:06:48,305
Why don't we just get rid
of all this...

45
00:06:48,349 --> 00:06:50,317
shit.

46
00:06:57,458 --> 00:07:00,427
[Footsteps]

47
00:07:31,459 --> 00:07:33,324
That's how
I want to remember him,

48
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,521
you know, before he moved
into this house, and...

49
00:07:39,333 --> 00:07:42,427
Katie, I think
that you should know that the...

50
