196
00:18:59,446 --> 00:19:02,415
[Ringing continues]

197
00:19:08,455 --> 00:19:11,424
[Haunting moaning]

198
00:19:32,412 --> 00:19:34,437
[Ringing continues]

199
00:19:38,318 --> 00:19:41,287
[Film hissing]

200
00:19:47,260 --> 00:19:48,488
[Water running]

201
00:20:05,445 --> 00:20:08,414
[Projector clicking]

202
00:22:05,398 --> 00:22:06,365
[Glass shatters]

203
00:22:06,433 --> 00:22:09,402
[Faint screaming]

204
00:22:15,342 --> 00:22:18,505
[Gasps]

205
00:22:18,545 --> 00:22:20,513
[Knife clatters]

206
00:22:36,496 --> 00:22:37,463
[Screams]

207
00:22:37,530 --> 00:22:39,293
[Shushes]

208
00:22:39,332 --> 00:22:40,424
I heard somebody
moving around.

209
00:22:40,433 --> 00:22:42,401
Oh, sorry.

210
00:22:42,435 --> 00:22:44,494
What are you doing up?

211
00:22:44,537 --> 00:22:46,300
Are you all right?

212
00:22:46,339 --> 00:22:48,500
[Sighs]

213
00:22:48,541 --> 00:22:51,510
I was sleepwalking again.

214
00:23:01,488 --> 00:23:02,455
If you resist me,

215
00:23:02,522 --> 00:23:05,252
you may find
the church against you.

216
00:23:09,262 --> 00:23:11,492
They could hang you!

217
00:23:11,531 --> 00:23:13,294
Sorry?

218
00:23:13,333 --> 00:23:14,425
Your line.

219
00:23:14,467 --> 00:23:17,265
"They could hang you
for your infidelity. "

220
00:23:17,303 --> 00:23:18,292
I just thought that...

221
