Maybe you should read
the script.

226
00:23:30,483 --> 00:23:32,451
I can't watch.

227
00:23:34,387 --> 00:23:36,480
She only got the part because,
you know, her brother...

228
00:23:43,430 --> 00:23:44,454
[grunts]

229
00:23:44,464 --> 00:23:46,432
[Screams]

230
00:24:00,280 --> 00:24:02,271
They don't know
what they' re talking about.

231
00:24:02,348 --> 00:24:04,509
