because of your brother.

232
00:24:06,386 --> 00:24:08,286
Thanks.

233
00:24:08,288 --> 00:24:10,415
I just thought
you should know.

234
00:24:10,457 --> 00:24:13,358
Why do you think
I got the part?

235
00:24:17,263 --> 00:24:20,232
Probably...

236
00:24:20,300 --> 00:24:21,324
because she left it
up to me.

237
00:24:21,334 --> 00:24:22,494
Stop messing around.

238
00:24:22,535 --> 00:24:24,332
You don't believe me?

239
00:24:24,370 --> 00:24:25,394
No, I'm not gullible.

240
00:24:25,438 --> 00:24:29,465
Well...

241
00:24:29,509 --> 00:24:31,443
