253
00:25:54,327 --> 00:25:56,295
Shit.

254
00:26:05,338 --> 00:26:07,306
Hello?

255
00:26:09,442 --> 00:26:11,376
[Sighs]

256
00:26:17,417 --> 00:26:19,385
Kathryn?

257
00:26:19,419 --> 00:26:22,388
[Theatrical music
plays over speakers]

258
00:26:34,534 --> 00:26:36,399
[Objects clattering]

259
00:26:53,252 --> 00:26:54,344
Hello?

260
00:27:12,505 --> 00:27:14,336
[Yells]

261
00:27:29,489 --> 00:27:31,354
Mom?

262
00:27:34,327 --> 00:27:35,419
[Screams]

263
00:27:35,461 --> 00:27:38,521
[Groaning]

264
00:27:38,531 --> 00:27:40,499
[Gasps]

265
00:27:46,472 --> 00:27:49,236
[Screams]

266
00:27:49,308 --> 00:27:52,277
[Demon roaring]

267
00:28:15,501 --> 00:28:18,470
[Percussive music]

268
00:28:18,504 --> 00:28:27,344
# #

269
